Product Deep Dive: Buzzbaits - Buzzbait season is here, and we want to break down some key features of our Tour Toad Buzz and Suicide Shad Buzz. 
• The sound of a buzzbait is probably the most important part, and ours can be tuned to clack or not without impacting the bait's ability to plane quickly and run true. 
• Blade color can make a big difference in triggering bites, and we have options to match every situation and every plastic.
• Double wire keeper for holding whatever plastic you put on.
• Super sharp Mustad UltraPoint hook that will keep fish pinned when it matters most!
• Available in 1/4oz and 3/8oz, these are a great option to catch fall fish!! #productdeepdive #buzzbaits #fallfishing #bigbitebaits
